00:01:08.665 --> 00:01:12.577
So, it's going to be
three minus two times,

00:01:12.577 --> 00:01:13.738
we're taking f-prime of four,

00:01:13.738 --> 00:01:17.303
so minus two times four

00:01:17.303 --> 00:01:20.704
over x-squared.

00:01:20.704 --> 00:01:24.705
So that's going to be
four-squared, minus k,

00:01:24.705 --> 00:01:28.146
is three times four,

00:01:28.146 --> 00:01:31.873
three times four, and then
we square that whole thing.

00:01:31.873 --> 00:01:33.440
